function_test_distance module

This module defines three tests for the distance_to function defined in the function_calculate_distance module.

function_test_distance.test_continent()

Test distant calculation for airports in different continents.

function_test_distance.test_error_code()

Test if function identifies invalid ICAO codes.

function_test_distance.test_same()

Test if function can handle airports with same location.
